{"tid":798690,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【高登新聞】馮盈盈上高登被發現 某媒體指鹿為馬造成交通事故","createTime":"2018-08-29T12:59:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-02T00:34:16.000Z","uid":61080,"like":27,"dislike":75,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"31760edfd16c289c14e23f761850644278cd2f35","tid":798690,"uid":61080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T12:59:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/29/UGzE1C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F29%2FUGzE1C.png&h=e89d2c45&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n高登新聞片段:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/3_WHvQvrzOY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F3_WHvQvrzOY&d=c%2BU9SroH3bzlC3xuuhKPfC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=58cde465\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/3_WHvQvrzOY</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【高登新聞】馮盈盈上高登被發現，某媒體指鹿為馬造成嚴重交通事故<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">較</span>早前某媒體於Facebook上發佈一張馮盈盈上高登圖，指高登討論區為坊間某山寨討論區，其報導引起大批巴打關注，有會員甚至找出當時馮盈盈正在瀏覽高登哪篇帖文，亦有路邊社指鄰近有山寨討論區出現嚴重交通事故，因道路濕滑觸發連環撞爆車頭燈災難。<br />\n<br />\n事件反映現今有個別傳媒公司已經脫離傳統傳媒枷鎖，看破紅塵，視公信力如無物。<br />\n<br />\n隨後記者訪問馮盈盈當時使用的高登討論區手機程式開發者織菊防gay，他表示：&quot;爽啊，估唔到fyy都會用我&quot;<br />\n<br />\n(高登新聞 達萌西/高登記者 報道)<br />\n<br />\nSource:<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=HT&amp;message=6949984\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Ftype%3DHT%26message%3D6949984&d=c%2BU9SroH3bzlC3xuuhKPfC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=22d66b6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=HT&amp;message=6949984</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n支持兒登:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n支持高登:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b3e79fd0e6950cf66e62641a407954f5754c8bd","tid":798690,"uid":61080,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T13:03:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\